title: G’Day LA fashion showcase: Foreign Minister Julie Bishop revels with Rebel Wilson
text:
JULIE Bishop unleashed her inner fashionista in LA yesterday in support of the country’s top designers.
All eyes were on the Foreign Minister when she stepped out on the ruby rug laid out at the G’Day LA Australian Fashion Showcase in a risque long-sleeved black midi-dress with a boundary- pushing cut-out on the chest.
Bishop officially opened the annual initiative, which encourages economic ties between Australia and the US, before sitting front row to view local labels.
Also in the crowd at Union Station in downtown LA were Aussie actors Rebel Wilson and Hugh Sheridan .
